~ start
There are too many guards out there. But there is a shortcut.
Do you want me to fix the bridge for you?
- Yes => help_accepted
- No => help_denied

~ help_accepted
do FixBridge.fix_bridge()
Bye!
do GameState.global.clear_help()
=> END

~ help_denied
OK, bye!
=> END
